data.title: Daily Newspaper - 2015 - 11 - 09 - 000000
data.meta_description:
Daily newspaper_2015_11_09_000000 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is an index page from a newspaper that includes summaries of articles on the following topics:

1. HH the Emir of Qatar chaired a meeting of the Supreme Council for Economic Affairs and Investment. 

2. The National Human Rights Committee and Primary Health Care Corporation will launch a campaign on the right to health.

3. A World Bank report warned that climate change could increase poverty and disease without action to reduce it. 

It also provides a very brief summary of two additional articles on a defeat for Modi's alliance in Indian elections and the Russian plane crash investigation in Egypt.
